The paper discusses query processing over big data, which is a common topic in the database community (cs.DB). The authors also mention resource efficiency and lower operational costs, which are relevant to distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper proposes learning cost models, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG). The authors also mention workload patterns, which are relevant to data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses integrating the learned cost models within the query optimizer, which is a software engineering problem (cs.SE).
